text: HTC One M9 is smartphone developed by HTC. It was announced on March 1, 2015. It was released around the world on April 10, 2015. It has 32GB storage, 3GB RAM, 5.0 inch Super LCD screen, 20MP back camera, 4MP front camera and 2840mAh battery capacity. == Reviews == Wired reviewing HTC One M9, it has good reviews like very good screen, very good battery, beautiful phone and able to customize the phone so much, it has bad reviews like camera cannot keep up yet. == References == Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2015 Category:HTC mobile phones
title: HTC One M9
